Package org.apache.wayang.core.optimizer.enumeration

Class PlanEnumerator

java.lang.Object
org.apache.wayang.core.optimizer.enumeration.PlanEnumerator
public class PlanEnumerator extends Object
The plan partitioner recursively dissects a WayangPlan into PlanEnumerations and then assembles them.
